{"tid":753022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【係精神嘅】O記派臥底搗破倫敦金騙案拘48人","createTime":"2018-07-23T09:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T07:24:44.000Z","uid":54337,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"eea2ddd2951fa9278c8bd2a4e6d8a977ecb15d56","tid":753022,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"O記派臥底搗破倫敦金騙案拘48人<br />\n<br />\n警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科(O記)於2年前開始，派出臥底混入倫敦金集團搜證，動員超過200人，並於前日展開拘捕行動，拘捕48人，警方將於稍後交代案情。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方本月亦拘捕多人涉與倫敦金騙案有關。警方在本月11日，展開「斷風行動」，搗破倫敦金騙案集團，拘捕31人。至本月13及17日，再拘捕多4人，涉嫌「串謀詐騙」。35名被捕男女全數獲准保釋候查，8月中旬向警方報到。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/mobile/bkn-20180723165816536-0723_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180723165816536-0723_00822_001.html&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7c42bd77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/mobile/bkn-20180723165816536-0723_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0d27ee0517fac0ee773350abaf7848442837ffac","tid":753022,"uid":108236,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"精神！今個月爆數！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3469f4cb3554041fbf38f54f4b829a9b3f447fc","tid":753022,"uid":54337,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"倫敦金：阿蛇，你敢唔敢成功先？"},{"pid":"2a86db8c468f22862c0eac3c3a5ae52c375668e2","tid":753022,"uid":144774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d37f552f593e7a5b76a12914f1a04a1074edbe","tid":753022,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"O記仲放埋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ae5dfb19633fc4485354c126d61936e2ff71d8","tid":753022,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef66ccbd4898e2b059c962780c5cc8c32fbf08d","tid":753022,"uid":138006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"因為轉去呃人玩加密貨幣了。"},{"pid":"81d25abbaac07b275c5fc0319bf8add925eabda1","tid":753022,"uid":27250,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7ef66ccbd4898e2b059c962780c5cc8c32fbf08d","tid":753022,"uid":138006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"因為轉去呃人玩加密貨幣了。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"證明O記啲人去做倫敦金都唔會俾人覺得有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fce60b3c832689b04b820d8a71d43069e1b504","tid":753022,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"30fa88041a1ac4ee2a89299671b717efe0dcf0ba","tid":753022,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>【倫敦金騙案】金融MK扮女神呃巴打 O記卧底破倫敦金集團拉54人<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180723/58476651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58476651&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=70f37002\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58476651&h=b83f6d06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180723/58476651</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方再搗破倫敦金集團，有組織罪案及三合會調查科(O記)派出卧底成功滲入兩間公司，搜集證據，今日突擊掩至尖沙嘴及觀塘兩間公司拘捕54人，涉嫌串謀詐騙。<br />\n<br />\n警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科聯同毒品調查科、商罪科、 網絡安全及科技罪案調查科及機動部隊，出動超過200名警員，今日分別於尖沙嘴及觀塘兩間倫敦金公司拘捕54人，分別49男5女(16至38歲)，當中包括兩間公司的董事、股東、負責人及經紀，涉嫌串謀詐騙及洗黑錢。行動中，警方撿獲大批現金、電腦、手機、銀行卡及虛假交易文件。另外，警方亦凍結兩間公司合共3部名車，包括有2部保時捷及一部平治，市值約500萬元的住宅物業以及18個銀行戶口。警方相信是次行動已成功瓦解兩個倫敦金集團。<br />\n<br />\n警方振示，涉案公司租用甲級寫字樓用作培訓及見客，以假冒國際金融集團名義招聘年輕人加入，主管負責教導如果利用投資賺取高額佣金。被捕男子多為男性，他們在網上社交平台假扮女性，並聲稱投資可獲巨額回報，吸引網民投資，再騙取對方簽署授權書，全權交予他們交易。當騙徒獲得授權後，即不斷與公司的虛擬程式交易，收取佣金榨乾受害人的金錢。受害人亦無法得知自己戶口情況，該公司亦會不斷轉名及轉地址，以逃避警方追查。<br />\n<br />\nO記早前派出卧底滲入上述兩間公司，獲聘為經紀，其間參與會議，得悉公司運作及計劃，蒐集夠證據後，今日成功拘捕多名涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n警方於本月共動員300人搜查多間公司及住宅，包括位於北角電氣道183號灝天金融集團及灣仔告士打道151號天裕控股集團的辦公室，拘捕至少35男女，包括公司高層，涉嫌串謀詐騙。35名被捕人士已獲准保釋，8月中向警方報到。"},{"pid":"c835913eb444117f8ce7a522af63e196638c5a23","tid":753022,"uid":49009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:33:30.000Z","msg":"👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻"},{"pid":"20d979c8828105e8f4ac8a20e159b575ea181516","tid":753022,"uid":29084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf3798f26b9ebfa9052087e5a7a28144b062501","tid":753022,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"希望告得入"},{"pid":"bdd365b40f9bd4dd9596bf07d7116226ad609e10","tid":753022,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5dd8bf070c5de203f6bec28bbc71907f681cfc","tid":753022,"uid":6329,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bdd365b40f9bd4dd9596bf07d7116226ad609e10","tid":753022,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"49男 5女<br />\n好多都係男扮女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02dac7f7a2265eb05c462e8d2898868598fb287","tid":753022,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"16至38歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未夠18歲已經係金融才俊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721a4293cde977f20b27e83f5acfb7d21070aceb","tid":753022,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acf3798f26b9ebfa9052087e5a7a28144b062501","tid":753022,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"希望告得入"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"有卧底就易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢班金融才俊洗定屎忽"},{"pid":"a5d52cd3142c736995ec956485d07b777283ec70","tid":753022,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"照咁睇應該係捉佢地無真係做trade就收佣<br />\n佢地真係有做就可以繼續呃落去"},{"pid":"b4b584bee999f2a5a426687111c4fa178812517b","tid":753022,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:21:33.000Z","msg":"收到風搵錢果班走晒，淨返祭旗嘅得返d on9 mk仔"},{"pid":"1a7de805a8663641970eccc70bcd411ce604cb09","tid":753022,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:23:19.000Z","msg":"返工返到比警察拉<br />\n係精神既"},{"pid":"c3730ac3d1d19371d639fe3a2c9169129245d356","tid":753022,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"721a4293cde977f20b27e83f5acfb7d21070aceb","tid":753022,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acf3798f26b9ebfa9052087e5a7a28144b062501","tid":753022,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"希望告得入"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"有卧底就易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢班金融才俊洗定屎忽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180323/mobile/bkn-20180323163750353-0323_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180323%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180323163750353-0323_00822_001.html&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a64d14fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180323/mobile/bkn-20180323163750353-0323_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n甩左"},{"pid":"b68d9ad89187082d73a9682d394265474a6c4333","tid":753022,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0e5cb3b81daba37ba2cd8e2688554bdab062b09","tid":753022,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"比條LAN線佢地自己解決喇 冇人會怪差佬今次"},{"pid":"556c3c75d35e34cf3f44167b581a3bba8d3b80aa","tid":753022,"uid":106810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"講真一日d人咁蠢哩d事只會持續<br />\n<br />\n哩d本身都唔係咩好人，有無底無所謂<br />\n<br />\n下一浪倫敦金請人，隨時要求有相關案底，底薪會高d"},{"pid":"427a44e4aa4826ad9fadc1616adc2882d6ad2304","tid":753022,"uid":111253,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"d mk同臥底阿蛇講精神, 阿蛇會唔會忍唔住笑"}]}